GoPaste
=======

NOTE: This software is in a pre-alpha stage of development and should
not be put into production.

What is it?
-----------

GoPaste is a very minimal clone of pastebin, a web service that lets
you paste chunks of code and get a permanent URL that will let you
view it in the future, formatted properly.

Requirements
------------

Unix.

Installation
------------

Download the compiled binary, put it somewhere on your PATH and run it.

